Search-Glimpse
==============

This module interfaces with glimpse to be used directly from Perl.
At the moment is simply a hack. Ideas are welcome.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IO::File


